      "span_text": "30 μl of MTT (5 mg/ml) was added to incubate for 4 h at 37 o C. The supernatant was discarded and the formazan crystal was dissolved with DMSO (100 μl/well). The absorbance was measured at 570 nm using a microplate reader (Thermo Scientific) [CITATION_1] ."
